Ep: Know No BetterArtist: Major LazorGenre: Electronic dance music, DancehallRelease: June 2Before releasing their upcoming studio album &ldquo;Music is the Weapon&rdquo;, Major Lazor have a prequel EP that probably is a glimpse into what to expect. The trio features artists from various genres such as Quavo, J Balvin, Sean Paul, Nasty C, Patoranking, Jidenna, Busy Signal, Anitta, Pabllo Vittar, Machel Montano and Konshens. The musical dialogue seems to be getting stronger with Major Lazor, who are recruiting artists from America, Africa and Jamaica to release essential hits such as &ldquo;Know No Better,&rdquo; &ldquo;Particula&rdquo; and &ldquo;Jump&rdquo;. The EP is a compilation of club-destined hits that will make just want to dance. We can&rsquo;t wait for the actual album to drop. Star rating: 3.5 out of 5